# =====================
# REPORTS
# =====================

### Submit Report (protected - uses user_id from token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reports
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location_id": 1,
  "noise_level": 3,
  "crowd_level": "low"
}

###

### View Reports for Location 1 (last 7 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations/1/reports?days=7

###
